movies.Title: Star Wars: Episode III - Revenge of the Sith
movies.Overview: Three years into the Clone Wars, the Jedi rescue Palpatine from Count Dooku. As Obi-Wan pursues a new threat, Anakin acts as a double agent between the Jedi Council and Palpatine and is lured into a sinister plan to rule the galaxy.

movies.Title: Star Wars: Episode IV - A New Hope
movies.Overview: Luke Skywalker joins forces with a Jedi Knight, a cocky pilot, a Wookiee and two droids to save the galaxy from the Empire's world-destroying battle station, while also attempting to rescue Princess Leia from the mysterious Darth Vader.

movies.Title: The Lord of the Rings: The Fellowship of the Ring
movies.Overview: A meek Hobbit from the Shire and eight companions set out on a journey to destroy the powerful One Ring and save Middle-earth from the Dark Lord Sauron.

movies.Title: Solo: A Star Wars Story
movies.Overview: During an adventure into the criminal underworld, Han Solo meets his future co-pilot Chewbacca and encounters Lando Calrissian years before joining the Rebellion.

movies.Title: Star Trek: First Contact
movies.Overview: The Borg travel back in time intent on preventing Earth's first contact with an alien species. Captain Picard and his crew pursue them to ensure that Zefram Cochrane makes his maiden flight reaching warp speed.

movies.Title: Jumanji: Welcome to the Jungle
movies.Overview: Four teenagers are sucked into a magical video game, and the only way they can escape is to work together to finish the game.

movies.Title: Austin Powers: International Man of Mystery
movies.Overview: A 1960s secret agent is brought out of cryofreeze to oppose his greatest enemy in the 1990s, where his social attitudes are glaringly out of place.
